@startuml
autonumber
skinparam BoxPadding 10
skinparam ParticipantPadding 10
skinparam BackgroundColor #ffffff
skinparam RoundCorner 4

skinparam ActorBorderColor #b4975a
skinparam ActorBackgroundColor #fcfbf7
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #b4975a
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #fcfbf7
skinparam DatabaseBorderColor #b4975a
skinparam DatabaseBackgroundColor #fcfbf7
skinparam ArrowColor #b4975a

actor "Client Manager" as User

box "Client App (Mobile / Web)" #LightBlue
  participant "HMI Stars App" as App
end box

box "Supabase Backend" #LightGreen
  participant "GoTrue Auth Engine" as Supabase
end box

actor "SMTP Mail Server" as Mail

== Step 1: Initiate Email Change ==
User -> App : Input new email address
activate App
App -> Supabase : updateUser(email: newEmail)
activate Supabase
Supabase -> Mail : Dispatch OTPs to old & new email
activate Mail
Mail --> User : Deliver OTP codes to both mailboxes
deactivate Mail
Supabase --> App : Return OTP status (needs confirmation)
deactivate Supabase
App --> User : Render OTP Input screen
deactivate App

== Step 2: Verify Old Email OTP ==
User -> App : Input OTP 1 (sent to old_email)
activate App
App -> Supabase : verifyOTP(email: oldEmail, token: otp1, type: emailChange)
activate Supabase
Supabase --> App : Return status: need_new_email_verification
deactivate Supabase
App --> User : Prompt for OTP 2 (sent to new_email)
deactivate App

== Step 3: Verify New Email OTP ==
User -> App : Input OTP 2 (sent to new_email)
activate App
App -> Supabase : verifyOTP(email: newEmail, token: otp2, type: emailChange)
activate Supabase
Supabase --> App : Confirm email update (Complete)
deactivate Supabase
App --> User : Show success toast notification
deactivate App

@enduml
